  18 May 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> alex-2.0.ebuild:
  Changed app-text/tetex to virtual/tetex.

  25 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> alex-2.0.ebuild:
